12-[1-(3,4-dihydroxycyclohexyl)prop-1-en-2-yl]-17-ethyl-1,14-dihydroxy-23,25-dimethoxy-13,19,21,27-tetramethyl-11,28-dioxa-4-azatricyclo[22.3.1.04,9]octacos-18-ene-2,3,10,16-tetrone and tris(1-methylindol-5-yl)bismuthane react together in the presence of ethaneperoxoic acid, acetate, dichloromethane, copper(2+) to produce 17-ethyl-1,14-dihydroxy-12-[1-[3-hydroxy-4-(1-methylindol-5-yl)oxycyclohexyl]prop-1-en-2-yl]-23,25-dimethoxy-13,19,21,27-tetramethyl-11,28-dioxa-4-azatricyclo[22.3.1.04,9]octacos-18-ene-2,3,10,16-tetrone.

tert-butyl N-[1-(6-fluoropyridin-3-yl)ethyl]carbamate and molecular iodine react together in the presence of oxolane, oxidane, lithium;2-methylpropane to produce tert-butyl N-[1-(6-fluoro-4-iodopyridin-3-yl)ethyl]carbamate.
6-methyl-1,3-benzothiazol-2-amine and di(imidazol-1-yl)methanethione react together in the presence of acetonitrile to produce N-(6-methyl-1,3-benzothiazol-2-yl)imidazole-1-carbothioamide.
